OL,5, The family of a former rugby player is 
OL,6, highlighting the risk of dementia      
OL,7, related to multiple small head         
OL,8, injuries, after he died last year.     
OL,10,FPeter Jones developed dementia in his  
OL,11,F50s and died aged 71.                  
OL,13,FA post-mortem examination revealed it  
OL,14,Fwas caused by repeated head blows.     
OL,16,FHis family has joined a class action   
OL,17,Fagainst various sporting bodies for    
OL,18,Ffailing to protect him from the risks  
OL,19,Fcaused by concussion. The WRU has been 
OL,20,Fasked to comment.                      
